title: Internal Compiler error building Sierra example

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:

### Code

```Rust
fn main(){
    println!("Hello World");
}
```

### Crate toml (see https://github.com/zakarumych/sierra/blob/master/demo/Cargo.toml)
```toml
[package]
name = "rust-vulkan"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["C0D3 M4513R <28912031+C0D3-M4513R@users.noreply.github.com>"]
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
sierra = { version = "=0.4.1", features = ["proc-verbose-docs"] }
scoped-arena = "0.4"
eyre = "0.6"
color-eyre = "0.6"
tracing = "0.1"
tracing-error = "0.2"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3"
winit = "0.26"
```
